<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-17932] Distcp file length comparison have no effect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-17932</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the params for compareFileLengthsAndChecksums in RetriableFileCopyCommand have no effect&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;current is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        DistCpUtils.compareFileLengthsAndChecksums(source.getLen(), sourceFS,
                sourcePath, sourceChecksum, targetFS,
                targetPath, skipCrc, source.getLen());&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; void compareFileLengthsAndChecksums(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; srcLen,
           FileSystem sourceFS, Path source, FileChecksum sourceChecksum,
           FileSystem targetFS, Path target, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; skipCrc,
           &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; targetLen) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (srcLen != targetLen) {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IOException(
        DistCpConstants.LENGTH_MISMATCH_ERROR_MSG + source + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; (&quot;&lt;/span&gt; + srcLen
            + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;) and target:&quot;&lt;/span&gt; + target + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; (&quot;&lt;/span&gt; + targetLen + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;so, compare source.getLen() with source.getLen()...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be like below in history view&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        DistCpUtils.compareFileLengthsAndChecksums(source.getLen(), sourceFS,
                sourcePath, sourceChecksum, targetFS,
                targetPath, skipCrc, offset + bytesRead);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
